		<h2 class="entry-title"><a href="https://ma.tt/2018/09/snaps-along-the-camino/" rel="bookmark">Snaps Along the&nbsp;Camino</a></h2>	</header><!-- .entry-header -->

	
		<figure class="post-thumbnail">
			<a class="post-thumbnail-inner" href="https://ma.tt/2018/09/snaps-along-the-camino/" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1">
				<img width="604" height="270" src="https://i2.wp.com/ma.tt/files/2018/09/IMG_8656.jpg?fit=604%2C270&amp;ssl=1" class="attachment-post-thumbnail size-post-thumbnail wp-post-image" alt="" srcset="https://i2.wp.com/ma.tt/files/2018/09/IMG_8656.jpg?resize=604%2C270&amp;ssl=1 604w, https://i2.wp.com/ma.tt/files/2018/09/IMG_8656.jpg?zoom=2&amp;resize=604%2C270 1208w, https://i2.wp.com/ma.tt/files/2018/09/IMG_8656.jpg?zoom=3&amp;resize=604%2C270 1812w" sizes="(max-width: 34.9rem) calc(100vw - 2rem), (max-width: 53rem) calc(8 * (100vw / 12)), (min-width: 53rem) calc(6 * (100vw / 12)), 100vw" data-attachment-id="48446" data-permalink="https://ma.tt/2018/09/snaps-along-the-camino/img_8656/" data-orig-file="https://i2.wp.com/ma.tt/files/2018/09/IMG_8656.jpg?fit=4032%2C3024&amp;ssl=1" data-orig-size="4032,3024" data-comments-opened="1" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;1.8&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;iPhone XS&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;1538041116&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;4.25&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;250&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0.016666666666667&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}" data-image-title="IMG_8656" data-image-description="" data-medium-file="https://i2.wp.com/ma.tt/files/2018/09/IMG_8656.jpg?fit=840%2C630&amp;ssl=1" data-large-file="https://i2.wp.com/ma.tt/files/2018/09/IMG_8656.jpg?fit=640%2C480&amp;ssl=1" />			</a>
		</figure>

			
	<div class="entry-content">
		<p>I walked a week&#8217;s worth of the Portuguese path of the Camino de Santiago with a few friends, which was a nice bookend <a href="https://ma.tt/2017/01/rebirth-and-yellow-arrows/">to my Rebirth and Yellow Arrows post</a> at the beginning of last year. My feet are sore, and I have the first significant knee pain which has given me newfound empathy for the people I love who struggle with their knees. I traveled light and just brought an iPhone XS as my camera, and these are a few snaps of things I saw along the trail.</p>
<p> <a href="https://ma.tt/2018/09/snaps-along-the-camino/#more-48371" class="more-link">Continue reading<span class="screen-reader-text"> &#8220;Snaps Along the&nbsp;Camino&#8221;</span></a></p>
	</div><!-- .entry-content -->

	<footer class="entry-footer">
		<span class="byline"><svg class="svg-icon" width="16" height="16" aria-hidden="true" role="img" focusable="false" viewBox="0 0 24 24" version="1.1" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><path d="M12 12c2.21 0 4-1.79 4-4s-1.79-4-4-4-4 1.79-4 4 1.79 4 4 4zm0 2c-2.67 0-8 1.34-8 4v2h16v-2c0-2.66-5.33-4-8-4z"></path><path d="M0 0h24v24H0z" fill="none"></path></svg><span class="screen-reader-text">Posted by</span><span class="author vcard"><a class="url fn n" href="https://ma.tt/author/saxmatt/">Matt</a></span></span><span class="posted-on"><svg class="svg-icon" width="16" height="16" aria-hidden="true" role="img" focusable="false" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><defs><path id="a" d="M0 0h24v24H0V0z"></path></defs><clipPath id="b"><use xlink:href="#a" overflow="visible"></use></clipPath><path clip-path="url(#b)" d="M12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12s4.5 10 10 10 10-4.5 10-10S17.5 2 12 2zm4.2 14.2L11 13V7h1.5v5.2l4.5 2.7-.8 1.3z"></path></svg><a href="https://ma.tt/2018/09/snaps-along-the-camino/" rel="bookmark"><time class="entry-date published" datetime="2018-09-29T14:35:13-07:00">September 29, 2018</time><time class="updated" datetime="2018-10-09T13:07:17-07:00">October 9, 2018</time></a></span><span class="cat-links"><svg class="svg-icon" width="16" height="16" aria-hidden="true" role="img" focusable="false" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M10 4H4c-1.1 0-1.99.9-1.99 2L2 18c0 1.1.9 2 2 2h16c1.1 0 2-.9 2-2V8c0-1.1-.9-2-2-2h-8l-2-2z"></path><path d="M0 0h24v24H0z" fill="none"></path></svg><span class="screen-reader-text">Posted in</span><a href="https://ma.tt/category/gallery/" rel="category tag">Gallery</a></span><span class="comments-link"><svg class="svg-icon" width="16" height="16" aria-hidden="true" role="img" focusable="false" viewBox="0 0 24 24" version="1.1" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><path d="M21.99 4c0-1.1-.89-2-1.99-2H4c-1.1 0-2 .9-2 2v12c0 1.1.9 2 2 2h14l4 4-.01-18z"></path><path d="M0 0h24v24H0z" fill="none"></path></svg><a href="https://ma.tt/2018/09/snaps-along-the-camino/#comments">6 Comments<span class="screen-reader-text"> on Snaps Along the&nbsp;Camino</span></a></span>	</footer><!-- .entry-footer -->
